<section class="landing youre-not-the-only-one-with-questions numbered">
    <div class="section-number">
     <span aria-hidden="true">04</span>
     <span class="visually-hidden">Section 4</span>
   </div>

  <div class="arrow-container top mobile" aria-hidden="true">
    <%=
      render ArrowComponent.new(
        width: 150,
        height: 200,
        x1: 0,
        y1: 0,
        x2: 0.9,
        y2: 0.9,
        cx: 0.7,
        cy: 0.2,
        arrow_size: 0.06
      )
    %>
  </div>

  <div class="arrow-container top desktop" aria-hidden="true">
    <%=
      render ArrowComponent.new(
        width: 300,
        height: 100,
        x1: 0,
        y1: 0,
        x2: 0.9,
        y2: 0.9,
        cx: 0.3,
        cy: 1,
        arrow_size: 0.05
      )
    %>
  </div>

  <%= image_pack_tag("static/images/content/hero-images/english.jpg", **image_alt_attribs("static/images/content/hero-images/english.jpg")) %>


  <div class="text">
    <h2>
      <span class="blue no-wrap">
        You're not the only
      </span>
      <br>
      <span class="blue no-wrap blend">
        one with questions.
      </span>
    </h2>

    <p class="blue">
      We know you’re sure to have questions - maybe even a few concerns – about
      teaching. It’s only natural. But you’re not alone. It’s a big decision
      and every year, thousands of people like you ask the same questions.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="questions">
    <div class="intro">
      Here’s what some recently qualified teachers have to say about
      these questions.
    </div>
    <div class="questions-and-answers">
      <div class="question-and-answer">
        <p class="q">
          What's the salary like?
        </p>

        <figure class="a">
          <blockquote>I know some people worry about the pay, especially when they start out. But my career progression has been really fast. Becoming a teacher is worth it.</blockquote>

          <figcaption>Jacqui</figcaption>
        </figure>
      </div>

      <div class="question-and-answer">
        <p class="q">
          What’s the work balance like?
        </p>

        <figure class="a">
          <blockquote>I sometimes do a couple of hours at the weekend so I'm ready for the week ahead. But I try to keep my weekends free to make sure I have some real downtime.</blockquote>

          <figcaption>Sarah</figcaption>
        </figure>
      </div>

      <div class="question-and-answer">
        <p class="q">
          Will I have the confidence?
        </p>

        <figure class="a">
          <blockquote>At the start of my training I felt like I didn’t have the authority to be standing up here and asking them to behave a certain way for me&hellip; but it is a confidence thing and now going into my last placement, I feel completely confident with it&hellip; it just comes with time. There’s so much support along the way.</blockquote>

          <figcaption>Amy</figcaption>
        </figure>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="arrow-container bottom mobile" aria-hidden="true">
    <%=
      render ArrowComponent.new(
        width: 200,
        height: 200,
        x1: 1,
        y1: 0,
        x2: 0.1,
        y2: 0.9,
        cx: 0.3,
        cy: 0.3,
        arrow_size: 0.065
      )
    %>
  </div>

  <div class="arrow-container bottom desktop" aria-hidden="true">
    <%=
      render ArrowComponent.new(
        width: 500,
        height: 400,
        x1: 1,
        y1: 0.25,
        x2: 0.3,
        y2: 0.85,
        cx: 0.4,
        cy: 0.1,
        arrow_size: 0.04
      )
    %>
  </div>
</section>
